{"title":"sed匹配某一行开头,替换整行内容","date":"2019-06-13T15:42:22.000Z","link":"post/345","tags":["Linux sed"],"categories":["Linux"],"updated":"2019-06-13T15:38:18.586Z","content":"<h2 id=\"原数据\">原数据<a href=\"post/345#原数据\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">CORE_LIBS = 1111</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"替换语句\">替换语句<a href=\"post/345#替换语句\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sed -i '/^CORE_LIBS/cCORE_LIBS = \\\"$CORE_LIBS -L/usr/lib -lfastcommon -lfdfsclient\\\"' /usr/local/src/fastdfs-nginx-module/src/config</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"替换后\">替换后<a href=\"post/345#替换后\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">CORE_LIBS = \"$CORE_LIBS -L/usr/lib -lfastcommon -lfdfsclient\"</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"Centos7下docker安装fastdfs","link":"post/344"},"next":{"title":"Vue 通过if判断绑定style","link":"post/343"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/345/","toc":[{"title":"原数据","id":"原数据","index":"1"},{"title":"替换语句","id":"替换语句","index":"2"},{"title":"替换后","id":"替换后","index":"3"}]}